{"tid":1792062,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃藍大戰大家千其唔好入場支持，會出事","createTime":"2019-12-21T10:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T11:19:31.000Z","uid":208122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e972a318d77b620ebcebc9939372808718488b10","tid":1792062,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"黃藍大戰大家千其唔好入場支持，會出事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港超<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>大戰</span></strong></span></span><br />\n香港人撐完港足，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好當港超係CONDOM</span></span></strong>。<br />\n一定要出錢出力入場撐港超，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復足球文化圈</span></strong></span></span><br />\n成日話假日香港冇地方好去冇野好做，依家就同我入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩聽就同我推上去同埋入場睇，淨係需要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">$20</span></strong>就入場睇到<br />\n<br />\n理文對東方龍師 黃藍大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期日 12月21日 下午2:30<br />\n深水埗運動場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>$20特惠，$60正常票價</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港由重建港足文化開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3IWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=65949eec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wurZPYe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwurZPYe.jpg&h=d04927bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3201b9511770a0078f6a0ecf73e01c53f84d6fea","tid":1792062,"uid":165871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":